** {{IPA|/əkˈsent/}}

====Verb====
{{en-verb}}

# {{transitive}} To express the accent of (either by the voice or by a mark); to utter or to mark with accent.
# {{transitive}} To mark emphatically; to emphasize; to accentuate.
# {{transitive}} To mark with written accents.

